    <div>
      <h2 class="h2">Recommended page structure</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Album overview / context</li>
        <li>What period of Charlotte’s practice it represents</li>
        <li>Key themes, collaborators, or production decisions</li>
        <li>Track-by-track notes that explain the journey of each song</li>
        <li>Optional links to press, performance clips, or related documentation</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="h2">Writing prompt</h2>
      <p class="small">Aim for short, specific notes rather than long reflection. A few sentences per track is enough: what sparked it, what changed through drafting/production, and what place it holds on the album.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

